name: .TNEF File Extension
summary: Learn about .TNEF files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: Microsoft Outlook (Windows, Mac) and KMail (Linux) support the TNEF format. You can use these email clients to view messages that include TNEF files and retrieve any attachments the TNEF files contain.
You can also use tnef2win (Windows), TNEF's Enough (Mac, iOS), or KTNEF (Linux) to extract data from TNEF files.
